rows.label: tlk70000043_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew...
Another day of overfilling my belly.

rows.label: tlk70000043_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But, I'm no' done eating yet! The
delicacies and finery of Iiran cooking
aren't just about fillin' your face!

rows.label: tlk70000043_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Until I get to savor a legendary dish
from that famous chef, my trip cannot
be over!

rows.label: tlk70000043_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I came all the way from Superbia
to tickle my tastebuds with her
legendary tastes!

rows.label: tlk70000043_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm going to get me some of
Ms. Sorrel's cooking and make this
trip worth my while!
